name: Black heart
description:
One day he saw himself and understood that he was tired of being alone, he thought and saw that the dragon, who is the king of the sea, is the only one who has high social status and can be his friend.
So he went to the dragon and said: king, I realized that you are very lonely and I thought to myself that I will not leave you alone and I came here to tell you that you can be my friend.
The dragon turned to him and said: I have many friends and I can be with one of them at any time, but governance rules does not give me the opportunity to explore.
But when I look at your pus and black, I realize that you are arrogant and probably alone.
Heart, who had been hit so hard, angrily left the king's palace, but he was a little confused.
